<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الْقَارِعَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَارِعَةُ (١)</span> مَا الْقَارِعَةُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الْكَلَامُ فِي أَوَّلِهَا مِثْلُ الْكَلَامِ فِي أَوَّلِ الْحَاقَّةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(يَوْمَ يَكُونُ النَّاسُ كَالْفَرَاشِ الْمَبْثُوثِ (٤)</span>) .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(يَوْمَ يَكُونُ)</span> : الْعَامِلُ فِيهِ الْقَارِعَةُ، أَوْ مَا دَلَّتْ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقِيلَ:</span> التَّقْدِيرُ: اذْكُرُوا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٍ رَاضِيَةٍ (٧)</span>) .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَ <span class="c2">(رَاضِيَةٍ)</span> : قَدْ ذُكِرَ فِي الْحَاقَّةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَأُمُّهُ هَاوِيَةٌ (٩)</span> وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا هِيَهْ <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> نَارٌ حَامِيَةٌ <span class="c2">(١١)</span>) .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالْهَاءُ فِي <span class="c2">«هِيَهْ»</span> : هَاءُ السَّكْتِ، وَمَنْ أَثْبَتَهَا فِي الْوَصْلِ أَجْرَى مَجْرَى الْوَقْفِ لِئَلَّا تَخْتَلِفَ رُءُوسُ الْآيِ. وَ <span class="c2">(نَارٌ)</span> : خَبَرُ مُبْتَدَأٍ مَحْذُوفٍ؛ أَيْ هِيَ نَارٌ <span class="c2">«حَامِيَةٌ»</span> .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>